title: Neewer Led CN-126 Ultra High Power 126 LED Digital Camera / Camcorder Video Light
description:
Description:This 126 LED Video Light can adapt to different types of digital video camcorders and cameras. It can also work as Office table lamp, industrial lamp, power cut light, or even Barbecue at your garden, etc.Compatible batteries (not included)Sony NP-Series Li-ion rechargeable battery (NP-FH70, NP-FM55H, NP-F550...)Panasonic CGR-D16S rechargeable battery6 x Alkaline/NiMH AA BatterySpecification:LED Quantity: 126 piecesInput: DC 7.4-8.4VMaximum Power: 7.56 WattColor Temperature: 5400K (3200k w/filter)NOTE:Please turn off the power after use. In order to avoid waste of battery an longtime heat generation and further affect the service life of LED bulbsIf power is supplied by AA battery ,please remove the battery when the LED Lighting is out of use. Otherwise, the battery unused longtime will go moldy and rot the ciruit inside the LED LightingPlease install battery as gently as you can to avoid damage and distortion of the battery holder.package contents:1 x LED Video Lighting 
3 x Filters
1 x Battery holder
1 x Hot shoe stand
